## Output

The engine **replaces** the `## PD-C-8. 目的妥当性確認` section in `current-note.md` with your output. Emit exactly this one `##` section (no other top-level headings):

### `## PD-C-8. 目的妥当性確認`

Body must include, in this order:

- **Verdict:** `pass` or `reject`
